commands:
**I know the following commands:**
`1.` help: Shows this list of commands.
`2.` version: Displays my current version.
`3.` say: Makes me say stuff and deletes your message.
`4.` ping: Displays the current latency to the Discord API and my client.
`5.` eval: (Owner Only) Evaluates JavaScript.
`6.` shutdown: (Owner Only) Shuts the bot down.
